[gd_scene load_steps=6 format=3]

; Slice β (2026-04-24) — Garden zone primitive scaffold. A single stone
; lantern (cylinder post + flat cap) and a gravel base suggest the roji
; approach without authoring the full stepping-stone sequence; the stone
; lantern piece itself doubles as the shared motif with Rikyū's chashitsu
; approach and placeholder for future roji stepping stones. The
; Blender-authored .glb eventually replaces this build.
;
; Scene root sits at (33.33, 0, 33.33) to match ``ZONE_CENTERS[GARDEN]``
; (``+WORLD_SIZE_M / 3`` on X and Z). Keep in sync with ``world/zones.py``
; and ``BoundaryLayer.gd``.

